      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Discover The Best Free Government Cell Phones!</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. What Are Free Government Cell Phones?</h4>\n<img alt=\"Discover The Best Free Government Cell Phones!_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones/discover-the-best-free-government-cell-phones_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Free government cell phones are phones provided by the government to low-income households. The program is called the Lifeline Assistance Program and provides eligible households with a free cell phone, monthly minutes and texts. In addition, the Affordable Connectivity Program can help by providing low-cost internet service and devices.</p>\n</img></div>"
